    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, along with some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear, and while all major electronics are functional, a few minor interior trim pieces are loose. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It has been regularly serviced, and we have records for the last three years of maintenance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
